highlights.text: “Si Me Necesitas, Llámame” by Siloé has been on Viral Songs Spain the longest, at 92 days straight.
“ZAZA - Remix” by El Sie7e, D´Flow Aka La Maldad, Rony Alca, and Duglaung is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Spain, up 16 spots at #44.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Spain. “Golden” is the highest at #6.
“Dame Un Grrr - Provi Remix Radio Edit” by Fantomel, Kate Linn, and Provi is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Spain at #27.
